        authType - (optional) Identifies which user authentcation method will be used.
        groupSearchBaseDN - (optional) The base DN of the tree to start the group search (will do a subtree search from here).
        groupSearchCustomFilter - (optional) REQUIRED for CustomFilter
        groupSearchType - (optional) Controls the default group search filter used, can be one of the following:
        searchBindDN - (optional) REQUIRED for SearchAndBind
        searchBindPassword - (optional) REQUIRED for SearchAndBind
        serverURIs - [required] A list of LDAP server URIs (examples: "ldap://1.2.3.4" and ldaps://1.2.3.4:123")
        userDNTemplate - (optional) REQUIRED for DirectBind
        userSearchBaseDN - (optional) REQUIRED for SearchAndBind
        userSearchFilter - (optional) REQUIRED for SearchAndBind.

        NoGroups: No group support.
        ActiveDirectory: (default) Nested membership of all of a user's AD groups.
        MemberDN: MemberDN style groups (single-level).
